ge=&#8221;2552&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; el_class=&#8221;hide-mobile-only&#8221;]<\/div><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][\/vc_section][vc_section 0=&#8221;&#8221;][vc_row el_id=&#8221;graduatevisa&#8221;][vc_column][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;64px&#8221;][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;64px&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Graduate Visa (485)<\/h4>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=&#8221;1556&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; el_class=&#8221;show-mobile-only-new&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">If you have completed your study and looking for next option we can assist you with Graduate Visa. This visa will let you work in Australia for limited time period depending on your qualification. You can work, study and travel during this period.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row 0=&#8221;&#8221;][vc_column 0=&#8221;&#8221;]<div class=\"columns_wrap sc_columns columns_nofluid sc_columns_count_2\"><div class=\"column-1_2 sc_column_item sc_column_item_1 odd first\"><h4 class=\"sc_title sc_title_regular sc_align_left\" style=\"text-align:left;color:#e23400;\">Details<\/h4>[vc_column_text 0=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>You must be under 50 years of age.<\/li>\n<li>You are the main holder of a current student visa.<\/li>\n<li>You held a student visa within the past 6 months before your application and now hold a substantive visa.<\/li>\n<li>You successfully completed all course requirements.<\/li>\n<li>You completed your course as a result of at least two academic years (92 weeks) of study.<\/li>\n<li>Overall score of IELTS at least 6 with a minimum score of 5 for each of the 4 parts.<\/li>\n<li>Overall score of PTE at least 50 with a minimum score of 36 for each of the 4 parts<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text]<\/div><div class=\"column-1_2 sc_column_item sc_column_item_2 even\">[vc_single_image image=&#8221;1556&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; el_class=&#8221;hide-mobile-only&#8221;]<\/div><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row el_id=&#8221;visitorvisa&#8221;][vc_column][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;64px&#8221;][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;64px&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Visitor Visa (Subclass 600)<\/h4>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=&#8221;1547&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; el_class=&#8221;show-mobile-only-new&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">If you want to visit Australia then we assist you with VISITOR VISA. This visa can let you visit Australia as tourist,to see family and friends, or for other purpose like any business or medical treatment.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row 0=&#8221;&#8221;][vc_column 0=&#8221;&#8221;]<div class=\"columns_wrap sc_columns columns_nofluid sc_columns_count_2\"><div class=\"column-1_2 sc_column_item sc_column_item_1 odd first\"><h4 class=\"sc_title sc_title_regular sc_align_left\" style=\"text-align:left;color:#e23400;\">Eligibility<\/h4>[vc_column_text 0=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Visit family or friends.<\/li>\n<li>You can also visit as a tourist.<\/li>\n<li>You can study or train for up to 3 months in total on this visa. But if your main reason for travelling to Australia is study, a student visa might be more appropriate.<\/li>\n<li>You must have, or have access to, enough money to support yourself while you are in Australia.<\/li>\n<li>You can\u2019t over stay.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text]<\/div><div class=\"column-1_2 sc_column_item sc_column_item_2 even\">[vc_single_image image=&#8221;1547&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; el_class=&#8221;hide-mobile-only&#8221;]<\/div><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][\/vc_section]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_se